<div class="container my-4">

  <!-- Title Row -->
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="display-4">A Litany of Survival</h1>
      <h4 class="text-muted">By Audre Lorde</h4>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Row 1: Audre Lorde image + stanza 1 -->
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 mb-3">
      <div class="box p-3 text-center bg-light">
        <img src="audre_lorde.jpg" alt="Audre Lorde" class="img-fluid rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
      <div class="box p-3 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <p>For those of us who live at the shoreline standing upon the constant edges of decision, crucial and alone, for those of us who cannot indulge the passing dreams of choice...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Row 2: Galaxy image + stanza 2 -->
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 mb-3">
      <div class="box p-3 text-center bg-light">
        <img src="galaxy.jpg" alt="Galaxy Dreams" class="img-fluid rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
      <div class="box p-3 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <p>For those of us who were imprinted with fear like a faint line in the center of our foreheads, learning to be afraid with our mother’s milk...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Row 3: Rosie the River + multiple stanzas -->
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 mb-3">
      <div class="box p-3 text-center bg-light">
        <img src="rosie_river.jpg" alt="Rosie the River" class="img-fluid rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 mb-3">
      <div class="box p-3 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <p>And when the sun rises we are afraid it might not remain...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="box p-3 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <p>And when the sun sets we are afraid it might not rise in the morning, when our stomachs are full we are afraid of indigestion...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Row 4: Sunset image + final stanza -->
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-12">
      <div class="box p-3 text-center bg-light">
        <img src="sunset.jpg" alt="Sunset" class="img-fluid rounded">
        <p class="mt-3">So it is better to speak, remembering we were never meant to survive.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
